<h2>Audio:</h2>

<p>Displays directories and files stored on memory card and internal storage of the device. Displays only audio files of the supported formats and directories, where they are located. For navigation use joystick buttons or programmable “1-9” buttons.  To navigate between the pages of the bookshelf use a joystick buttons left/right. To open desired file, press the appropriate number button, or select the file with the joystick and then press “OK” button.</p>
<p>To return to the previous menu, press “С” button.</p>
<p>To return to the main menu, press “MENU” button.</p>
<p>To change the screen orientation (portrait/landscape), press “Rotate” button in the lower left bottom side of the device. </p>
<p>To call help, press “0” button.</p>
<p>You can call bookshelf menu if you press “М” button.</p>
<p>To open the previously displayed files, proceed to the “Recent files” menu. In the “Favorites” menu the list of the previously added files to favorites are displayed.</p>
